dct_alternative_sm: Port Nepui (Mueo) to Isle of Pines
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by soundings; heights by hachures and spot heights.
Includes 2 profile views and 2 inset charts.
Shows shoals, reefs, drainage, coastal relief, small islands.
"Excluding the plans of Port Nepui and Moindu Bay, the longitudes of all points on this chart should be decreased 40"."
